data.description: This stunning 4 bed, 3 bath home located in highly acclaimed Windsong Ranch is perfect for entertaining friends and family. Enjoy the backyard oasis with outdoor living with lush landscaping, fire pit and hot tub. As you enter the expansive foyer, you are greeted by the study, perfect for an in-home office or exercise room. Adjacent lies a secluded secondary bedroom complete with a walk-in closet and access to a full-size bathroom. The family room features a gorgeous fireplace, views of the outdoor living area and overlooks the kitchen. Gourmet kitchen offers a center island, ample counter space, with large walk-in pantry. The main bedroom is the perfect retreat featuring an amazing en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, soaking tub and spacious walk-in closet. A magnificent curved staircase takes you to the second floor where you will find a generous-sized game room, two more secondary bedrooms with walk-in closets and a shared full-size bathroom. 3 car garage with epoxy flooring.
